{"tid":2220824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳門《司法警察法》修訂案將生效　評論員憂白色恐怖","createTime":"2020-09-28T02:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T03:13:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"581e54618d8b5a33c2228e823966e839dbb7709e","tid":2220824,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"上月在澳門立法會通過的《司法警察法》修訂案，最爭議的是容許當局可以向行政長官申請，豁免公佈執行特殊任務的人員名單。當局解釋是為保護執法人員安全，因為他們要處理包括國家安全等較嚴重的罪行，有必要隱藏身份。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員蔡梓瑜說，法案猶如一把刀架在社會，尤其是年輕人頭上，令言論空間被收窄。他說已感到傳媒近期訪問只停留在民生雜事，很少觸及政治或社會制度。<br />\n<br />\n投票贊成法案的直選議員林玉鳯就認為，社會的憂慮是受香港政治氣氛和過往內地執法形象影響，她指出法律已平衡市民權益和執法人員安全，希望當局在法律生效後不要隨便引用，以免破壞社會仍然保持到的警民互信關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551965-20200928.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551965-20200928.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=db7418a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551965-20200928.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4d82db20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551965-20200928.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5fb824ca3cef284b85bd09a62ebb24bab239056c","tid":2220824,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"無事無幹都立啲鳩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />還是有事發生左只不過無公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0377d1206bf4b17bbae78b5ef571f5f4132cd6b","tid":2220824,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"澳門咁乖都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e20bd334a44cb8d77e64486d3400cbdcef4390","tid":2220824,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"澳門財